  "detailed_description": "<strong>Hero Survival</strong> is a roguelite game in which you will slay hordes of enemies from classic horror movies by enhancing your character, learning different skills and matching your play style with equipment.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Try to survive hordes of enemies</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/d728903b3b2fee784a018a65e41fa08e.poster.avif?t=1722467165\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/d728903b3b2fee784a018a65e41fa08e.webm?t=1722467165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/d728903b3b2fee784a018a65e41fa08e.mp4?t=1722467165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Face hundreds of classic horror monsters.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A very strange company of weirdos to play as</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/7466dfbd94c39059fb3445bad7d73db5.poster.avif?t=1722467165\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/7466dfbd94c39059fb3445bad7d73db5.webm?t=1722467165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/7466dfbd94c39059fb3445bad7d73db5.mp4?t=1722467165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Spend the coins earned in each run to unlock new characters. Get stronger, destroy thousands of enemies, survive wave after wave and try not to upset the Mad Time God!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Try out different builds in each run</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/cd7ddd01cebaf12c3cc1c8f4188aed52.poster.avif?t=1722467165\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/cd7ddd01cebaf12c3cc1c8f4188aed52.webm?t=1722467165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/cd7ddd01cebaf12c3cc1c8f4188aed52.mp4?t=1722467165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Choose a unique way for your character. Want to freeze your enemies? That's the cryomancer's way for you! Or would you rather play the role of a bomber who blows things up? Or maybe you're ready to rely only on your trusty weapon? Then you are a natural born gunslinger!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A lot of weapons and items to enhance your hero</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/bc20502b65099707845a6e6893553477.poster.avif?t=1722467165\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/bc20502b65099707845a6e6893553477.webm?t=1722467165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/bc20502b65099707845a6e6893553477.mp4?t=1722467165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Guns? Revolvers? Shotguns? Sniper rifles? Grenade launchers? Automatic rifles? Machine guns? We have them all!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 14 different weapons, from ordinary revolvers and submachine guns to legendary sniper rifles and grenade launchers<br></li><li> Dozens of different skills<br></li><li> Hundreds of item combinations to enhance your character<br></li><li> Your enemies are vampires, werewolves, mummies and other monsters from classic horror movies<br></li><li> Fast-paced runs<br></li><li> Waves of enemies, each one longer and fiercer than the last. How long will you last?</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Hero Survival</strong> is a roguelite game in which you will slay hordes of enemies from classic horror movies by enhancing your character, learning different skills and matching your play style with equipment.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Try to survive hordes of enemies</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/d728903b3b2fee784a018a65e41fa08e.poster.avif?t=1722467165\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/d728903b3b2fee784a018a65e41fa08e.webm?t=1722467165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/d728903b3b2fee784a018a65e41fa08e.mp4?t=1722467165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Face hundreds of classic horror monsters.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A very strange company of weirdos to play as</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/7466dfbd94c39059fb3445bad7d73db5.poster.avif?t=1722467165\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/7466dfbd94c39059fb3445bad7d73db5.webm?t=1722467165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247620/extras/7466dfbd94c39059fb3445bad7d73db5.mp4?t=1722467165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Spend the coins earned in each run to unlock new characters. Get stronger, destroy thousands of enemies, survive wave after wave and try not to upset the Mad Time God!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Try out different builds in each run</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"ht